name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Yokoe KABBAH, Petitioner

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 7th day of May, 2012, the Petition for Leave to File Petition for Allowance of Appeal Nunc Pro Tunc is GRANTED. Counsel is directed to file a Petition for Allowance of Appeal within 30 days of this order.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
